1. e4 c6 2. d4 d5 3. e5 c5 4. Nf3 {This is another critical line.} cxd4 $1 {
Although this is only the third choice for Black, I believe that this move
gives the best chances to equalize.} 5. Nxd4 (5. Qxd4 {This move does not make
