easily because there is this direct c4 push.} e6 {White got what he wanted,
however, with the catch that the b5-bishop is not ideally placed.} (6... Bf5 $2
7. c4 $1 {White has a very pleasant play.}) 7. O-O Nge7 8. c4 Bd7 9. Qg4 a6 10.
