1. e4 c6 2. d4 d5 3. e5 c5 4. dxc5 e6 5. Qg4 {This is the idea of the Great
Tal and was later tried by many strong grandmasters and a top player like MVL.}
h5 6. Qg3 (6. Bb5+ {This move seems dubious to me. After exchanging light
