Nh6 $1 {[%cal Gb8c6,Gh6g4] Black is ok.}) 7... Nc6 8. Nf3 f6 $5 $146 {This
looks very interesting to me, Black is directly attacking the center.} 9. Qg3 (
9. Bg6+ $6 Kf8 {The next move ...Nge7 will come with a tempo.} 10. Nbd2 Nge7
11. Bd3 Qc7 12. Nb3 Nxe5 $1 13. Nxe5 Bd6 $1 $17) (9. exf6 gxf6 {This is my
preference. Black has a very strong central pawns. Our king will be safe
