Kf7 16. Nxh8+ Qxh8 {Black surely will have enough compensation with such
central pawns and better piece placement.}) 11. Qh4 Kf7 $1 12. g4 $1 (12. O-O
$6 Nge7 $15 {[%cal Gd8g8,Gg8g4] Black is better.}) 12... e5 (12... Nb4 $5 {
