16. Bd1 (16. Be4 $6 f5 17. Bg5 Qc8 18. O-O-O fxe4 19. Qxe4 Qf5 20. Rxd4 Qxg5+
21. f4 exf4 $17) 16... f5 {The position is balanced.}) 9... Kf8 {Other moves
