can analyze it also yourself, but I prefer 10...Nf4 to have an easy play. That
was the reason I was delaying this ...Nc6 move for a long time.}) 11. c4 Nxd3
12. Qxd3 dxc4 13. Qxc4 Bd7 $1 {[%csl Gd7][%cal Gd7c6]} 14. Nbd2 $5 $146 {
